AB  - In order to improve the accuracy of trajectory of particles in quad-pole magnetic field, nonlinear effect of space charge was analyzed and calculated with Lie algebraic methods, the mapping formulas of particle coordinates through second order were obtained, and a computer code QML was written for the particle beam transmission in quad-pole magnetic field. QML was used to simulate particle beam transmission in quad-pole magnetic field, and the simulation results were analyzed. Simulation results indicated that, due to the influence of nonlinear effect of space charge, the beam phase diagram hadclear distortion, at the same time, the beam envelope had apparent lateral divergence.
