AB  - In this paper, a novel kind of algorithm, called the self-adaptive chaos quantum clonal evolutionary programming algorithms-SCQP, is proposed based on the quantum theory and the Chaos Mutation Operator. By adopting quantum chromosome as a representation, SCQP uses the Logistic Sequence to control the mutation size and the Chaos Mutation Operator to control the clonal selection. Compared with the classical evolutionary algorithm-CEA and SCQP, SCQP is shown to be a capable of solving complex machine learning tasks, and the experiment results are better.
